CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Kinetik Holdings Inc is a permian-to-gulf Coast midstream corporation operating in the Delaware Basin. It provides comprehensive gathering, transportation, compression, processing, and treating services for companies that produce natural gas, natural gas liquids, crude oil, and water.
